.MARINE...
(Today through Friday)
Issued at 439 AM PDT Sun Mar 29 2026

Moderate to fresh northerly winds continue across the outer waters
with locally strong gusts across the far northern outer waters.
Occasional fresh to strong gusts continue across the northern
waters through early Monday before winds diminish. Light rain is
possible Tuesday through Thursday. Hazardous conditions for small
crafts return mid to late week as significant wave heights build
and winds increase to near gale force.

